        </li>
        <li>
          Se le parti intere sono uguali, confronta le parti decimali cominciando dai decimi.<br>
          3,<span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">9</span> &gt; 3,<span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">5</span>26 perché <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">9</span> &gt; <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">5</span>
        </li>
